Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.80,0:01:38.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.95,0:01:41.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貓咪老師
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.38,0:01:44.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  跑哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.21,0:01:49.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.37,0:01:52.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼有去七{\fe128\fscx80\fscy92\fnDFPTFLeiSho-W5}辻{\r}屋的捷徑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.42,0:01:55.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這哪裏有條像樣的路啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.43,0:02:06.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天氣不錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.41,0:02:17.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目那傢伙  都叫他跟緊點了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.66,0:02:19.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是給我走散了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.65,0:02:21.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.44,0:02:24.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就等他5秒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.93,0:02:29.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1 2 3
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.97,0:02:47.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.51,0:02:50.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊  是貓嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.37,0:02:52.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別嚇我嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.86,0:02:53.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.83,0:03:00.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這丑貓是…  記得是夏目家的貓貓老師
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.39,0:03:02.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貓貓老師
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.78,0:03:03.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.76,0:03:04.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貓貓
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.97,0:03:07.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是很羞人的名字啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.71,0:03:08.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫你胖太算了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.95,0:03:09.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  胖太
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.09,0:03:10.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快起來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.21,0:03:12.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  胖太
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.50,0:03:15.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是貓咪老師  喂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.45,0:03:17.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是貓咪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.85,0:03:21.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  你是那個什麼田沼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.68,0:03:24.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是個傻瓜還挺能幹的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.96,0:03:26.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貓…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.51,0:03:27.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貓…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.51,0:03:29.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貓說話了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.60,0:03:37.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟…糟了  你還沒從夏目那裏聽說我的真實身份嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.46,0:03:44.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是妖怪啊  胖太
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.52,0:03:45.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是貓咪老師
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.41,0:03:47.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是妖怪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.91,0:03:52.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總體來說確實是的  不過我可是非常高貴的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.00,0:03:55.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要把我當成路邊的那種小妖混為一談
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.24,0:03:57.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這還是頭一回
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.44,0:04:01.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次能和妖怪交談  這還是我的頭一回
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.80,0:04:05.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此  你並不是能看到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.02,0:04:09.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以夏目才沒把我的事告訴你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.28,0:04:12.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你也幫不上什麼忙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.20,0:04:15.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.89,0:04:19.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.79,0:04:20.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.05,0:04:22.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是夏目的什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.82,0:04:23.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.04,0:04:27.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目是我收的小弟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.53,0:04:28.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小弟？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.77,0:04:31.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒有給夏目帶來困擾吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.56,0:04:33.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.19,0:04:36.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼看都是你比較像小弟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.03,0:04:38.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道不是你威脅了他嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.17,0:04:42.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙  隨便你說話就…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.79,0:04:45.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然知道了我的真實身份
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.62,0:04:48.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就必須要隱匿證據
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.10,0:04:50.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就開動了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.63,0:04:54.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹什麼啊  老師
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.40,0:04:57.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏…夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.03,0:05:03.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那隻貓為什麼會和你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.01,0:05:09.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師就像是我的保鏢一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.07,0:05:17.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目  不想說的話也沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.25,0:05:20.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.56,0:05:24.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為情況比較複雜  我也不知道該怎麼說明
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.84,0:05:28.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…並不是想瞞著田沼你的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.80,0:05:32.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不對  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.07,0:05:35.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我是想瞞著你的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.04,0:05:38.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我想和田沼你能正常的交談
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.66,0:05:41.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以不想讓你有不好的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.17,0:05:44.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有不好的回憶嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.53,0:05:50.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目  看吧  我抓到大魚了  看啊看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.76,0:05:53.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  也不是那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.92,0:05:59.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.87,0:06:02.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  是祭典  今晚會舉行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.70,0:06:05.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  秋季廟會嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.35,0:06:10.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也去看看吧  夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.65,0:06:12.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒準備完呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.51,0:06:14.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還在準備也沒關係  我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.57,0:06:17.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  等等啦  老師
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.32,0:06:24.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神社的話回去正好順路  我也一起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.43,0:06:26.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.77,0:06:31.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛  還沒好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.82,0:06:33.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不都說了還在準備嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.31,0:06:36.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還以為至少會有路邊攤的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.32,0:06:38.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.26,0:06:41.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fe128\fscx80\fscy92\fnDFPTFLeiSho-W5}屜{\r}田
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.78,0:06:48.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  還沒開始呢  有你的熟人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.18,0:06:50.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  倒不是這樣的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.30,0:06:52.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在幫忙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.52,0:06:55.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  因為受人之托
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.71,0:06:56.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.92,0:06:59.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有的吧…在這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.05,0:07:01.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有？ 你指什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.73,0:07:06.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別裝傻嘛  我聽說這種熱鬧的地方最容易聚集了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.35,0:07:08.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還在說這個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.62,0:07:13.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過嘛  確實  有很多
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.87,0:07:15.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猜中了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.01,0:07:17.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有些什麼樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.59,0:07:21.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小純  抱歉  幫我把這些搬到前殿那去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.70,0:07:23.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.79,0:07:27.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你  幫忙把那些搬到前殿去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.76,0:07:28.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.98,0:07:30.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.46,0:07:32.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還在聊天呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.60,0:07:34.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家拜託的是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.30,0:07:36.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別頂撞班長
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.95,0:07:38.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不是一個班的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.59,0:07:40.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那還是我去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.36,0:07:41.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目你別去啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.03,0:07:43.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小純
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.88,0:07:45.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個人等一下就會幫你拿過去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.44,0:07:46.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  喂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.45,0:07:47.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快一點
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.87,0:07:52.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我一下  我馬上就回來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.05,0:07:54.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  趁現在
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.50,0:07:55.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.94,0:08:08.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祭典的話  夏目一定也會來的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.32,0:08:11.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼搞的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.13,0:08:14.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天居然就是狐貍的姿態
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.33,0:08:16.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.92,0:08:19.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.04,0:08:26.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  竟然敢搗亂  你這小狐貍
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.09,0:08:30.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的  不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.59,0:08:34.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類是看不到我們的樣子的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.40,0:08:35.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好過分
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.56,0:08:38.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得我都快準備好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.83,0:08:40.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這混蛋  不可饒恕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.03,0:08:42.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的  不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.56,0:08:43.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.40,0:08:45.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要掙扎了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.26,0:08:49.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目  救救我  夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.26,0:08:52.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.68,0:08:55.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是太粗暴了點
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.84,0:08:57.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.47,0:08:59.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你沒關係吧  給我閃邊去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.89,0:09:01.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看到這狐貍弄翻的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.79,0:09:05.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看是沒看到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.47,0:09:07.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這裏只有它在吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.49,0:09:15.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來是風大呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.78,0:09:17.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開你的手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.77,0:09:27.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙看得到我們啊  怪物呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.35,0:09:29.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給  麥茶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.91,0:09:31.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  麻煩你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.69,0:09:34.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是空無一物到令人吃驚的地步啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.45,0:09:36.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  也沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.78,0:09:39.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間剛剛好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.76,0:09:43.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天花板的角落
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.97,0:09:44.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天花板？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.20,0:09:53.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.77,0:09:54.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.04,0:09:56.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是池塘反射上去的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.26,0:09:59.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.14,0:10:04.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庭院裏根本沒有池塘
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.65,0:10:11.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我覺得可能天花板上的水紋只有我們才能看得到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.05,0:10:14.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.33,0:10:16.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.31,0:10:18.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.44,0:10:19.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不可思議
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.87,0:10:26.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,田沼他看不到池塘啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.21,0:10:31.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.40,0:10:33.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.15,0:10:38.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉  被他跑掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.81,0:10:46.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目家的醜貓貓
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.14,0:10:50.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這孩子在我這的話  夏目就一定會回來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.79,0:10:52.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.07,0:10:57.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  有沒有繩子  呀  越牢越好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.16,0:11:01.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對  夏目  那不是鬍子  是肩胛骨
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.50,0:11:02.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.90,0:11:10.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.86,0:11:12.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.73,0:11:14.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你聽得懂我的話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.82,0:11:15.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.07,0:11:17.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你認識夏目嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.31,0:11:18.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.37,0:11:22.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  夏目也聽得懂我的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.09,0:11:26.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是來見那個人的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.71,0:11:29.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  他一定會來的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.75,0:11:32.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  能見到就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.25,0:11:36.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  那麼謝謝你了  再見
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.15,0:11:42.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fe128\fscx80\fscy92\fnDFPTFLeiSho-W5}柊{\r}  跟著它
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.84,0:11:43.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.68,0:11:52.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來遲了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.07,0:12:02.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失策了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.08,0:12:08.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就不能鎮靜點嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.74,0:12:13.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貴志他要直接去參加祭典的話告訴我們不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.67,0:12:15.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貴志又不是小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.50,0:12:18.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  萬一遇到事故的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.25,0:12:20.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還真是愛擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.82,0:12:23.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出了那種事  貓五郎會回來告訴我們的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.81,0:12:28.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要開玩笑啦  真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.74,0:12:34.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貴志來我們家有多久了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.02,0:12:39.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是一直以來留下了太多不好的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.08,0:12:42.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他也太客氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.69,0:12:48.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼隨便一點我也會輕鬆些
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.10,0:12:54.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼此之間都那麼客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.96,0:12:56.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不像一家人了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.85,0:12:57.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.85,0:13:10.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來得還是早了點呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.90,0:13:11.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.01,0:13:12.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.79,0:13:17.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼  別人掉的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.90,0:13:19.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我送過去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.95,0:13:24.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是有人掉落的東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.20,0:13:26.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了  先放在我這裏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.68,0:13:28.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.73,0:13:30.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.28,0:13:34.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  這個好像是別人掉的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.76,0:13:35.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.71,0:13:42.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小貓咪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.85,0:13:45.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  被抓住了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.17,0:13:48.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是做了什麼壞事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.58,0:13:52.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  民子來救你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.27,0:13:58.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被逃掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.12,0:14:09.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來幫幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.96,0:14:11.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.74,0:14:15.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不在呢  胖太
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.61,0:14:16.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.07,0:14:17.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胖太？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.42,0:14:20.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  我自言自語而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.14,0:14:22.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們分頭找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.50,0:14:25.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻煩你了  就這麼辦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.99,0:14:26.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.53,0:14:32.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找不到呢  錢袋子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.44,0:14:39.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想不起在哪裏掉的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.16,0:14:44.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裏面有那麼重要的東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.45,0:14:47.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  很重要
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.07,0:14:51.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.33,0:14:53.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去那邊也找找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.61,0:15:00.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去哪了呢  老師
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.69,0:15:02.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.04,0:15:04.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目  你果然也來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.39,0:15:09.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  貓咪老…不  有沒有看到我家的貓
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.79,0:15:10.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只胖貓嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.32,0:15:12.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒看到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.00,0:15:13.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.90,0:15:14.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它逃掉了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.80,0:15:15.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.83,0:15:16.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼回見
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.30,0:15:19.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給  久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.54,0:15:20.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.54,0:15:22.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.90,0:15:25.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔  我的回轉燒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.43,0:15:27.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼  我剛才不是給你了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.27,0:15:28.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒拿到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.67,0:15:29.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我給你了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.74,0:15:30.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快付錢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.79,0:15:32.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又沒拿到怎麼付你錢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.22,0:15:37.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.41,0:15:41.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  請問要多少錢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.79,0:15:53.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.85,0:15:58.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.82,0:15:59.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.72,0:16:01.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裏面到底放了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.67,0:16:02.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.37,0:16:04.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藥？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.72,0:16:07.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能讓我在一段時間內變成人類樣子的藥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.82,0:16:10.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直是獸型的話  會給夏目添麻煩的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.99,0:16:14.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此  是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.63,0:16:16.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  那麼就由我去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.29,0:16:27.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被食物的香味引誘來的嗎  小狐貍  不行的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.77,0:16:28.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去  去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.22,0:16:32.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.07,0:16:34.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.74,0:16:37.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.33,0:16:40.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.79,0:16:41.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它跑進來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.19,0:16:44.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.83,0:16:47.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  那我把它拿到山上放生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.10,0:16:49.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.54,0:16:51.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一等  我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.71,0:16:52.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.18,0:16:55.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的鍋煮沸了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.20,0:16:57.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.64,0:17:01.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真奇怪  我明明開的小火
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.89,0:17:08.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.06,0:17:11.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個樣子跑來人群裏可是很危險的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.06,0:17:16.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  可是  因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.17,0:17:18.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我給你拿來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.23,0:17:21.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.95,0:17:27.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.41,0:17:31.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fe128\fscx80\fscy92\fnDFPTFLeiSho-W5}柊{\r}  你在的話也就是說  名取先生他也在這嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.12,0:17:34.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧  他和人有約
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.95,0:17:37.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那個人拜託你跟著這孩子的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.00,0:17:39.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是毫無戒心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.76,0:17:43.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在沒有人煙的地方和我這樣的存在交談
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.74,0:17:45.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是會被人忌諱的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.97,0:17:46.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.59,0:17:50.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為…我是能看到的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.09,0:17:54.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個爛好人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.29,0:18:17.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…難道是剛才的小狐貍嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.17,0:18:20.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這位哥哥是好人啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.47,0:18:44.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於自由了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.36,0:18:48.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過夏目那傢伙  居然都不來救我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.81,0:18:49.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.45,0:18:54.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.85,0:19:00.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來  丑貓貓
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.35,0:19:04.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No～
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.29,0:19:12.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這附近確實有點冷呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.53,0:19:14.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧  不過很安靜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.70,0:19:21.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  夏目你是不是看到庭院裏的池塘了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.47,0:19:25.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我只能看到天花板上的倒影
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.06,0:19:30.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔子小姐知道嗎  你能看到這件事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.59,0:19:32.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.93,0:19:35.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不相信他們嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.11,0:19:36.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.80,0:19:43.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為他們很溫柔\N我覺得我說出來的話  他們一定會接受
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.98,0:19:46.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  也因為他們很溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.77,0:19:51.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會想到我一直以來的遭遇  為我心痛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.55,0:19:57.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然這樣想可能很自私  我不想他們那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.93,0:20:03.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望他們可以一直微笑下去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.19,0:20:09.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.20,0:20:15.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呵  比想像中還要棒嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.38,0:20:19.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還以為鄉下的話會更挫一點的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.80,0:20:20.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.13,0:20:21.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.91,0:20:23.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.70,0:20:29.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  其實我看不到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.74,0:20:33.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有個巨大的傢伙擋住我了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.64,0:20:37.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巨大的傢伙  妖怪嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.45,0:20:40.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  但我能感覺到很漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.19,0:20:44.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為它都看呆了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.00,0:20:49.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們走一段吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.88,0:20:52.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許有夏目你也能看清楚的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.79,0:20:55.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.64,0:21:08.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.55,0:21:12.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏的話可以看得清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.49,0:21:14.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.00,0:21:19.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些倒影裏的魚  其實是什麼顏色的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.63,0:21:23.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  是紅色的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.59,0:21:24.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅色
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.17,0:21:27.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.45,0:21:30.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在這裏啊  忘恩負義的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.61,0:21:32.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貓咪老師
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.96,0:21:36.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放著重要的保鏢不管  你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.74,0:21:37.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又升起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.79,0:21:57.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬天的腳步聲漸漸接近的秋夜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.63,0:22:01.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  這裏卻很溫暖
